  "title": "Dietetic Assistant (Healthcare) - Up to 3K #HHL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: Queenstown</strong><br /><strong>Working hour: 5 days office hour</strong><br /><strong>Salary: up to 3000</strong></p><p>Support dietitians by performing administrative and nutrition-related tasks to ensure smooth clinic operations and effective patient care.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare nutrition education materials and slides to support dietitian-led patient education</li><li>Manage appointment bookings, patient pre-clerking, and respond to phone enquiries to facilitate efficient clinic scheduling and communication</li><li>Assist in nutrition analysis, data entry, and statistical tasks to support research and reporting needs</li><li>Support quality improvement and outreach programmes by coordinating related activities and documentation</li><li>Manage oral nutrition supplement (ONS) samples to ensure availability and proper tracking</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Diploma in Applied Food Science & Nutrition</li><li>Communicate clearly with patients and team members to support customer service and clinic operations</li><li>Use basic IT skills (Word, Excel, PowerPoint) to prepare documents and manage data</li><li>Demonstrate familiarity with healthcare environments to adapt quickly to clinic workflows</li></ul><p>If interested, please email me at alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599).</p>",
